---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn how BestKarma turns credible health and longevity research into clear, practical guidance for real life."
>
  <section class="bg-cream-dark/60 border-b border-border">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <p class="text-sage-dark text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">About BestKarma</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-bark leading-tight">
        Live well. Age wisely.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-stone">
        BestKarma exists to turn credible health and longevity research into clear, practical guidance for ordinary life. The goal is simple: help people make better decisions, build better routines, and support healthier years ahead.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-cream-dark/50 p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-bark">What we cover</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-stone leading-relaxed">
          BestKarma focuses on the core systems that shape long-term health: longevity, nutrition, sleep, mind-body health, and sustainable daily routines.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-cream-dark/50 p-8">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-bark">How we work</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-stone leading-relaxed">
          We aim to publish content that is clear, practical, and science-backed. That means focusing on useful advice, citing sources, and keeping confidence proportional to the strength of the evidence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white p-8">
      <p class="text-sage-dark text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">
        Who's behind this
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-semibold text-bark">
        Built by Paresh Chauhan
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-stone leading-relaxed">
        I started BestKarma after years of reading health and longevity
        research and realising most of it never reaches the people who
        need it most &mdash; or reaches them wrapped in hype and supplement ads.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-stone leading-relaxed">
        I'm not a doctor or scientist. I'm someone who cares deeply about
        getting this right, which is why every article goes through a structured
        validation process with primary sources cited inline. BestKarma exists
        because I believe credible health information should be clear,
        accessible, and honest about what the evidence does and doesn't support.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-stone leading-relaxed">
        We're actively building a medical advisory board to strengthen our
        editorial review. Until then, transparency is our credibility &mdash;
        you can see exactly how every article is sourced and validated.
      </p>
      <a href="/editorial-standards"
         class="inline-block mt-4 text-sage-dark font-medium text-sm hover:text-sage transition-colors">
        Read our editorial standards &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 rounded-3xl bg-bark px-8 py-10 text-cream">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-semibold">What BestKarma is not</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-cream/75 leading-relaxed">
        We are not a substitute for a doctor, a supplement marketplace, or a source of miracle claims. When the evidence is mixed, we say so clearly.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm">
        <a href="/editorial-standards" class="rounded-full bg-sage px-5 py-2.5 font-medium text-cream hover:bg-sage-dark transition-colors">Read our standards</a>
        <a href="/blog" class="rounded-full border border-cream/20 px-5 py-2.5 font-medium text-cream hover:bg-cream/10 transition-colors">Browse articles</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
